## Authentication & Authorization

### JWT Security
```csharp
services.AddAuthentication(JwtBearerDefaults.AuthenticationScheme)
    .AddJwtBearer(options =>
    {
        options.TokenValidationParameters = new()
        {
            ValidateIssuer = true,
            ValidateAudience = true,
            ValidateLifetime = true,
            ValidateIssuerSigningKey = true,
            ClockSkew = TimeSpan.Zero, // ASLA default 5dk tolerans
            ValidIssuer = config["Jwt:Issuer"],
            ValidAudience = config["Jwt:Audience"],
            IssuerSigningKey = new SymmetricSecurityKey(key)
        };
    });
```

### JWT Token Standartlari
- Access Token: 15 dk (kisa omur)
- Refresh Token: 7 gun (secure, httpOnly cookie)
- Refresh Rotation: her kullanilda yeni token + eski iptal
- Claims: UserId, TenantId, Roles, Permissions (minimal)
- ASLA hassas veri JWT'ye koyma (sifre, kredi kart, TC)

### JWT Attack Vektorleri
| Saldiri | Onlem |
|---------|-------|
| Algorithm confusion (none/HS256) | ValidAlgorithms = ["RS256"] |
| Token theft (XSS) | HttpOnly + Secure + SameSite cookie |
| Brute force signing key | Min 256-bit key, key rotation |
| Token replay | jti claim + kisa omur |
| Privilege escalation | Server-side role check, ASLA client trust |

### 2FA (TOTP — RFC 6238)
- Uygulama: Google Authenticator / Microsoft Authenticator
- Backup codes: 10 adet, tek kullanimlik, bcrypt hash ile sakla
- Zorunluluk: Admin + yuksek yetkili kullanicilar icin ZORUNLU
- Rate limit: 5 hatali deneme -> 15 dk kilit

### Password Policy
```
MinLength: 12 karakter
Karmasiklik: Buyuk + kucuk + rakam + ozel karakter
Hash: BCrypt (cost factor: 12)
Gecmis kontrol: Son 5 sifre tekrar YASAK
HaveIBeenPwned: API ile bilinen sifreler YASAK
Degisim: 90 gunde bir (zorunlu degil, NIST 800-63B)
```

## OWASP API Security Top 10
```
API1: Broken Object Level Authorization (BOLA)
  -> Her endpoint'te object ownership kontrol et
API2: Broken Authentication
  -> Rate limit + account lockout + 2FA
API3: Broken Object Property Level Authorization
  -> DTO ile sadece izinli field'lari expose et
API4: Unrestricted Resource Consumption
  -> Rate limit + pagination limit + file size limit
API5: Broken Function Level Authorization
  -> [RequirePermission] attribute + RBAC
API6: Unrestricted Access to Sensitive Business Flows
  -> CAPTCHA + device fingerprint + bot detection
API7: Server Side Request Forgery
  -> URL whitelist + internal network block
API8: Security Misconfiguration
  -> Security headers + CORS strict + debug off
API9: Improper Inventory Management
  -> API versioning + deprecation policy + docs
API10: Unsafe Consumption of APIs
  -> Input validation on 3rd party responses
```

## Security Headers (ZORUNLU)
```csharp
app.Use(async (ctx, next) =>
{
    ctx.Response.Headers["X-Content-Type-Options"] = "nosniff";
    ctx.Response.Headers["X-Frame-Options"] = "DENY";
    ctx.Response.Headers["X-XSS-Protection"] = "0"; // modern browsers don't need
    ctx.Response.Headers["Strict-Transport-Security"] = "max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains";
    ctx.Response.Headers["Content-Security-Policy"] = "default-src 'self'; script-src 'self'";
    ctx.Response.Headers["Referrer-Policy"] = "strict-origin-when-cross-origin";
    ctx.Response.Headers["Permissions-Policy"] = "camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()";
    await next();
});
```

## Rate Limiting
```csharp
services.AddRateLimiter(options =>
{
    options.AddFixedWindowLimiter("general", opt =>
    {
        opt.PermitLimit = 100;
        opt.Window = TimeSpan.FromMinutes(1);
    });
    options.AddFixedWindowLimiter("auth", opt =>
    {
        opt.PermitLimit = 5;
        opt.Window = TimeSpan.FromMinutes(15);
    });
    options.RejectionStatusCode = 429;
});
```

## Threat Modeling (STRIDE)
```
S - Spoofing     -> Authentication (JWT, 2FA)
T - Tampering    -> Integrity (HMAC, digital signature, audit log)
R - Repudiation  -> Non-repudiation (audit trail, temporal tables)
I - Info Disclosure -> Confidentiality (encryption, TLS, data masking)
D - Denial of Service -> Availability (rate limiting, circuit breaker)
E - Elevation of Privilege -> Authorization (RBAC, least privilege)
```

