## Incident Response Plan
```
1. DETECT: Anomaly tespit (log alert, WAF, monitoring)
2. CONTAIN: Etkilenen hesaplari/servisleri izole et
3. ERADICATE: Root cause bul, vulnerability patch
4. RECOVER: Servisleri geri yukle, data integrity kontrol
5. LESSONS: Post-mortem yaz, kuralları guncelle
```

## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| Hardcoded secret | Environment variable / Key Vault |
| JWT'de hassas veri | Minimal claims |
| CORS: `*` | Explicit origin whitelist |
| `catch(Exception) {}` | Log + alert |
| Rate limit yok | Endpoint bazli rate limit |
| SQL string concat | Parameterized query |
| `ClockSkew = 5 min` | `ClockSkew = TimeSpan.Zero` |
